SELECT T1.*
FROM ABC400FIL.acfilext T1
WHERE T1.ACCLBE in @{item().cbcpy_list}
AND  T1.ACDTEE between int(@{pipeline().parameters.windowStart}) AND int(@{pipeline().parameters.windowEnd}) 
AND ACDTEE  <> 0 WITH UR

select t1.* 
from ABC400FIL.ATFXFRLOG t1
WHERE t1.XFRCLUBFROM in @{item().cbcpy_list} 
AND XFRCREATEDATE  between int(@{pipeline().parameters.windowStart}) AND int(@{pipeline().parameters.windowEnd}) with UR

SELECT a.*
FROM ABC400FIL.BCZFIL2 a
WHERE a.BCZCLB in @{item().cbcpy_list} with UR

SELECT a.*
FROM ABC400FIL.bczfil a
WHERE a.BCZCLB in @{item().cbcpy_list} with UR

CAST(t1.BPAVDCLB as VARCHAR(6))  as BPAVDCLB,
CAST(t1.BPAVDMBR as VARCHAR(6))  as BPAVDMBR,
CAST(t1.BPPRFCTR as VARCHAR(10))  as BPPRFCTR,
CAST(t1.BPINVAMT as VARCHAR(15))  as BPINVAMT,
CAST(t1.BPSTSDES as VARCHAR(25))  as BPSTSDES,
CAST(t1.BPCRPAMT as VARCHAR(15))  as BPCRPAMT,
CAST(t1.BPPDPAMT as VARCHAR(15))  as BPPDPAMT,
CAST(t1.BPTOTPRJ as VARCHAR(15))  as BPTOTPRJ,
CAST(t1.BPNMPINV as VARCHAR(15))  as BPNMPINV,
CAST(t1.BPCRIAVL as VARCHAR(15))  as BPCRIAVL,
CAST(t1.BPPDIAVL as VARCHAR(15))  as BPPDIAVL,
CAST(t1.BPTOTAVL as VARCHAR(15))  as BPTOTAVL,
CAST(t1.BPCRCOLL as VARCHAR(15))  as BPCRCOLL,
CAST(t1.BPCRCRFC as VARCHAR(15))  as BPCRCRFC,
CAST(t1.BPPDCOLL as VARCHAR(15))  as BPPDCOLL,
CAST(t1.BPPDCRFC as VARCHAR(15))  as BPPDCRFC,
CAST(t1.BPFTCOLL as VARCHAR(15))  as BPFTCOLL,
CAST(t1.BPFTCRFC as VARCHAR(15))  as BPFTCRFC,
CAST(t1.BPTOTRFCC as VARCHAR(15))  as BPTOTRFCC,
CAST(t1.BPTOTCOLL as VARCHAR(15))  as BPTOTCOLL,
CAST(t1.BPCRCHG as VARCHAR(15))  as BPCRCHG,
CAST(t1.BPCRRFC as VARCHAR(15))  as BPCRRFC,
CAST(t1.BPPDCHG as VARCHAR(15))  as BPPDCHG,
CAST(t1.BPPDRFC as VARCHAR(15))  as BPPDRFC,
CAST(t1.BPTOTCHG as VARCHAR(15))  as BPTOTCHG,
CAST(t1.BPTOTRFC as VARCHAR(15))  as BPTOTRFC,
CAST(t1.BPCRPCT as VARCHAR(14))  as BPCRPCT,
CAST(t1.BPPDPCTA as VARCHAR(14))  as BPPDPCTA,
CAST(t1.BPPDPCT as VARCHAR(14))  as BPPDPCT,
CAST(t1.BPTOTPCT as VARCHAR(14))  as BPTOTPCT
from ABC400FIL.bpdav2cldf t1
WHERE t1.BPAVDDTE >= 190101
AND t1.BPAVDDTE between int(@{pipeline().parameters.windowStart}) AND int(@{pipeline().parameters.windowEnd})
AND t1.BPAVDCLB in @{item().cbcpy_list}  WITH UR

SELECT a.*

AND    a.BPRCCLB in @{item().cbcpy_list} with UR

SELECT a.*

select distinct t3.YYMMDD as DateInput
from [StgIseries].ABC400FIL_DATECONV t2
join [StgIseries].ABC400FIL_DATECONV t3 on cast(EOMONTH(t2.the_date) as date)=t3.the_date 
where  t2.YYMMDD = 230328
order by 1

SELECT 
   CAST(a.BPDPMDTE as VARCHAR(20)) as BPDPMDTE,
   CAST(a.BPDPMCLB as VARCHAR(20)) as BPDPMCLB,
   CAST(a.BPDPMMBR as VARCHAR(20)) as BPDPMMBR,
   CAST(a.BPDPMFNM as VARCHAR(20)) as BPDPMFNM,
   CAST(a.BPDPMLNM as VARCHAR(20)) as BPDPMLNM,
   CAST(a.BPDPMPCCDE as VARCHAR(20)) as BPDPMPCCDE,
   CAST(a.BPDPMPCDES as VARCHAR(20)) as BPDPMPCDES,
   CAST(a.BPDPMPAM as VARCHAR(20)) as BPDPMPAM,
   CAST(a.BPDPMPDT as VARCHAR(20)) as BPDPMPDT,
   CAST(a.BPDPMPTP as VARCHAR(20)) as BPDPMPTP,
   CAST(a.BPDPMPGP as VARCHAR(20)) as BPDPMPGP,
   CAST(a.BPDPMPCD as VARCHAR(20)) as BPDPMPCD,
   CAST(a.BPDPMPDS as VARCHAR(20)) as BPDPMPDS,
   CAST(a.BPDPINV# as VARCHAR(20)) as BPDPINV#,
   CAST(a.BPDPABC$ as VARCHAR(20)) as BPDPABC$,
   CAST(a.BPDPABC@ as VARCHAR(20)) as BPDPABC@,
   CAST(a.BPDPMSEQ as VARCHAR(20)) as BPDPMSEQ,
   CAST(a.BPDPMSTA as VARCHAR(20)) as BPDPMSTA,
   CAST(a.BPDPMCFA as VARCHAR(20)) as BPDPMCFA,
   CAST(a.BPDPMBDT as VARCHAR(20)) as BPDPMBDT,
   CAST(a.BPDPMR1F as VARCHAR(20)) as BPDPMR1F,
   CAST(a.BPDPMTIM as VARCHAR(20)) as BPDPMTIM,
   CAST(a.BPDPMUSR as VARCHAR(20)) as BPDPMUSR,
   CAST(a.BPDPMBPF as VARCHAR(20)) as BPDPMBPF,
   CAST(a.BPDPMDPF as VARCHAR(20)) as BPDPMDPF,
   CAST(a.BPDPMCCT as VARCHAR(20)) as BPDPMCCT,
   CAST(a.BPDPMBAT as VARCHAR(20)) as BPDPMBAT,
   CAST(a.BPDPMCCN as VARCHAR(20)) as BPDPMCCN,
   CAST(a.BPDPMBRN as VARCHAR(20)) as BPDPMBRN,
   CAST(a.BPDPMR1S as VARCHAR(20)) as BPDPMR1S,
   CAST(a.BPDPDUDT as VARCHAR(20)) as BPDPDUDT
FROM ABC400FIL.BPDPMTDLY a
--JOIN ABC400FIL.cbfil b ON b.CBCLB = a.BPDPMCLB
--JOIN ABC400FIL.DATECONV  dt ON dt.YYMMDD = a.BPDPMDTE
WHERE  a.BPDPMDTE between int(@{pipeline().parameters.windowStart}) AND int(@{pipeline().parameters.windowEnd})
--WHERE b.CBCPY in @{item().cbcpy_list} and 
AND BPDPMCLB in @{item().cbcpy_list} with UR

SELECT 
CAST(T1.BPDPMDTE as VARCHAR(6))  as BPDPMDTE,
CAST(T1.BPDPMCLB as VARCHAR(5))  as BPDPMCLB,
CAST(T1.BPDPMMBR as VARCHAR(5))  as BPDPMMBR,
CAST(T1.BPDPMFNM as VARCHAR(15))  as BPDPMFNM,
CAST(T1.BPDPMLNM as VARCHAR(15))  as BPDPMLNM,
CAST(T1.BPDPMPCCDE as VARCHAR(10))  as BPDPMPCCDE,
CAST(T1.BPDPMPCDES as VARCHAR(30))  as BPDPMPCDES,
CAST(T1.BPDPMPAM as VARCHAR(15))  as BPDPMPAM,
CAST(T1.BPDPMPDT as VARCHAR(6))  as BPDPMPDT,
CAST(T1.BPDPMPTP as VARCHAR(1))  as BPDPMPTP,
CAST(T1.BPDPMPGP as VARCHAR(3))  as BPDPMPGP,
CAST(T1.BPDPMPCD as VARCHAR(3))  as BPDPMPCD,
CAST(T1.BPDPMPDS as VARCHAR(40))  as BPDPMPDS,
CAST(T1.BPDPINV# as VARCHAR(6))  as BPDPINV#,
CAST(T1.BPDPABC$ as VARCHAR(15))  as BPDPABC$,
CAST(T1.BPDPABC@ as VARCHAR(8))  as BPDPABC@,
CAST(T1.BPDPMSEQ as VARCHAR(5))  as BPDPMSEQ,
CAST(T1.BPDPMSTA as VARCHAR(15))  as BPDPMSTA,
CAST(T1.BPDPMCFA as VARCHAR(15))  as BPDPMCFA,
CAST(T1.BPDPMBDT as VARCHAR(6))  as BPDPMBDT,
CAST(T1.BPDPMR1F as VARCHAR(1))  as BPDPMR1F,
CAST(T1.BPDPMTIM as VARCHAR(6))  as BPDPMTIM,
CAST(T1.BPDPMUSR as VARCHAR(6))  as BPDPMUSR,
CAST(T1.BPDPMBPF as VARCHAR(1))  as BPDPMBPF,
CAST(T1.BPDPMDPF as VARCHAR(1))  as BPDPMDPF,
CAST(T1.BPDPMCCT as VARCHAR(1))  as BPDPMCCT,
CAST(T1.BPDPMBAT as VARCHAR(1))  as BPDPMBAT,
CAST(T1.BPDPMCCN as VARCHAR(16))  as BPDPMCCN,
CAST(T1.BPDPMBRN as VARCHAR(9))  as BPDPMBRN,
CAST(T1.BPDPMR1S as VARCHAR(5))  as BPDPMR1S
FROM ABC400FIL.BPDPMT T1
WHERE T1.BPDPMDTE between int(@{pipeline().parameters.windowStart}) AND int(@{pipeline().parameters.windowEnd})
AND BPDPMCLB in @{item().cbcpy_list}  WITH UR

SELECT 
CAST(T1.BPDCYCLE as VARCHAR(1))  as BPDCYCLE,
CAST(T1.BPDPRBDT as VARCHAR(6))  as BPDPRBDT,
CAST(T1.BPDPRCLB as VARCHAR(6))  as BPDPRCLB,
CAST(T1.BPDPRMBR as VARCHAR(6))  as BPDPRMBR,
CAST(T1.BPDPRFNM as VARCHAR(15))  as BPDPRFNM,
CAST(T1.BPDPRMI as VARCHAR(1))  as BPDPRMI,
CAST(T1.BPDPRLNM as VARCHAR(15))  as BPDPRLNM,
CAST(T1.BPDPRPCH as VARCHAR(1))  as BPDPRPCH,
CAST(T1.BPDPRCDE as VARCHAR(10))  as BPDPRCDE,
CAST(T1.BPDPRAMT as VARCHAR(15))  as BPDPRAMT,
CAST(T1.BPDPRPDT as VARCHAR(6))  as BPDPRPDT,
CAST(T1.BPDPRTYP as VARCHAR(1))  as BPDPRTYP,
CAST(T1.BPDPRAGE as VARCHAR(4))  as BPDPRAGE,
CAST(T1.BPD#INV as VARCHAR(3))  as BPD#INV  
FROM ABC400FIL.BPDPRJ T1
WHERE T1.BPDPRBDT >= 190101
AND T1.BPDPRCLB in @{item().cbcpy_list}
AND T1.BPDPRBDT between int(@{pipeline().parameters.windowStart}) AND int(@{pipeline().parameters.windowEnd})  WITH UR

SELECT a.*
FROM ABC400FIL.BPDTAX a
WHERE a.TXCLB in @{item().cbcpy_list} 
AND a.TXTODTE between int(@{pipeline().parameters.windowStart}) AND int(@{pipeline().parameters.windowEnd})  WITH UR

SELECT
	DFTCLB
	,DFTMBR
	,DFTLNM
	,DFTFNM
	,DFTMTC
	,DFTFDUE
	,DFTNDUE
	,DFTHPA
	,DFTHPP
	,DFTHPN
	,DFTSLM
	,DFTAGE
	,DFTTYP
	,DFTMDE
	,DFTFRQ
	,DFTSTS
	,DFTCNT
	,DFTCPN$
	,DFTDFT$
FROM ABC400FIL.BPMTDFTF T1
--INNER JOIN ABC400FIL.cbfil T2 ON T1.DFTCLB = T2.CBCLB
WHERE TO_DATE(CASE WHEN LENGTH(CAST(DFTFDUE AS VARCHAR(6))) <> 6 THEN LPAD (CAST(DFTFDUE AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0') ELSE CAST(DFTFDUE AS VARCHAR(6)) END,'DDMMYY') >= TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowStart, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI')  
AND   to_date(CASE WHEN LENGTH(CAST(DFTFDUE AS VARCHAR(6))) <> 6 THEN LPAD (CAST(DFTFDUE AS VARCHAR(6)),6,'0') ELSE CAST(DFTFDUE AS VARCHAR(6)) END,'DDMMYY') <  TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowEnd, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI') 
AND T1.DFTCLB in @{item().cbcpy_list}  with UR

select a.*
from ABC400FIL.BPSHDT a
--JOIN ABC400FIL.CBFIL b ON b.cbclb = a.BPSHCLB
where BPSHPDT>= TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowStart, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI') 
AND   BPSHPDT<  TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowEnd, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI') 
AND a.BPSHCLB in @{item().cbcpy_list}  with UR

SELECT a.*
FROM ABC400FIL.BPSMSTD2D1 a
WHERE a.BPSD2DCLB in @{item().cbcpy_list}
AND a.BPSD2DDTE between int(@{pipeline().parameters.windowStart}) AND int(@{pipeline().parameters.windowEnd})  WITH UR

SELECT DISTINCT 
CAST(t1.BPSMDXUID as VARCHAR(32))  as BPSMDXUID,
LEFT(CAST(t1.BPSMDXUTS as VARCHAR(19)),10)  as BPSMDXUTS,
CAST(t1.BPSMDXUIDX as VARCHAR(32))  as BPSMDXUIDX,
CAST(t1.BPSMDXCLB as VARCHAR(6))  as BPSMDXCLB,
CAST(t1.BPSMDXMBR as VARCHAR(6))  as BPSMDXMBR,
CAST(t1.BPSMDXSEQ as VARCHAR(6))  as BPSMDXSEQ,
CAST(t1.BPSMDXITM as VARCHAR(3))  as BPSMDXITM,
CAST(t1.BPSMDXDTE as VARCHAR(8))  as BPSMDXDTE,
UPPER(CAST(t1.BPSMDXNME as VARCHAR(30)))  as BPSMDXNME,
CAST(t1.BPSMDXAMT as VARCHAR(9))  as BPSMDXAMT,
CAST(t1.BPSMDXPCT as VARCHAR(7))  as BPSMDXPCT,
CAST(t1.BPSMDXPCF as VARCHAR(13))  as BPSMDXPCF,
CAST(t1.BPSMDXMTF as VARCHAR(11))  as BPSMDXMTF,
CAST(t1.BPSMDXALL as VARCHAR(13))  as BPSMDXALL
from ABC400FIL.BPSMSTDTLX T1
where BPSMDXUTS > TO_DATE('20181231','YYYYMMDD')
AND BPSMDXUTS >= TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowStart, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI')  
AND  BPSMDXUTS <  TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowEnd, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI')
AND T1.BPSMDXCLB in @{item().cbcpy_list} WITH UR
